data.description: Amazing 3,824 sqft. Executive home features 6 Bedrms, 3.5 Baths, Formal Living Rm and Formal Dining Rm, Eat-in Kitchen, Granite, Island, Pantry. Study, 1/2 Bath and Great Room downstairs.  All 6 bedrooms and 3 full baths are upstairs. Hardwood floors throughout downstairs, granite and tile in Kitchen and Baths.  Main suite with Walk in Closet, jetted tub and separate shower and dual sinks. 2 Car Attached Garage and 4 Car Detached Garage with water and electric, over-height garage doors and huge storage space upstairs that could be finished to create additional living space. Low maintenance vinyl exterior, mature landscaping. Energy efficient windows, 3-zone heating and cooling with 15 SEER HP. 6-in ext. walls.  Roof replaced by previous owner, one HVAC unit replaced by previous owner, most windows replaced 2018 by previous owner.  Kitchen cabinets,counters updated 2017 by previous owner. Gorgeous large front porch, large Deck plus Screened Porch! $10,000 Buyer CC with acceptable offer!
